Get free icons in Color design style

Color is a bright decorative style of the diverse flat icon pack. These color icons will fit any desktop, web application, or mobile app screen.


As well as Cute Color, Hand Drawn Color, and Circle Bubbles icon packs, they will effectively work as clipart images for infographics, custom cards, or presentations. Download our free color icons in different themes for your UI and graphic design needs. They are pixel-perfect and are available in both PNG and SVG formats.
